STONEAGE -- created after a roghly boulderdash-like AmigaBASIC game

This is currently non-functional pre-alpha software, so a detailed
description will follow later.


VERSIONING SCHEME:

n.m.x: alpha version aimed at beta version (n+1).(m+1)

n.x: beta version aimed at release version (n+1).0

n.0: Release version n.


SCM-POLICIES:

- use GNU autotools
- keep any autotools-generated files out of the VCS
- use doxygen to document AT LEAST the header files

